{"tid":975656,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"[年經] 同事個個月請病假，可以點做?","createTime":"2019-01-09T22:03:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-10T05:54:45.000Z","uid":67203,"like":7,"dislike":141,"uniUserReply":66,"replies":[{"pid":"7b446738b8debe74d0818d83a9e04ef3cd5ea96b","tid":975656,"uid":67203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T22:03:00.000Z","msg":"做緊服務性行業，一個月總有幾日特別忙<br />\n有個同事每月最忙嗰段日子揀兩三日請sick leave<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n由於啲野唔可以留到佢病完返黎先做 (客唔會第二日先黎..），所以規矩就係要第二個同事幫手頂<br />\n而我就係被<span style=\"color: blue;\"><del>神</del></span>呀頭選中要做埋呢個仆街射波同事嗰份嘅細路<br />\n<br />\n有人會話「依家又唔係做公司隻狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我有醫生紙請假關你撚事咩」<br />\n問題依家佢射波搞到我個個月有幾日要做double野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 做撚死我<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴絲打有類似情況? 我可以點對付佢? <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有諗過以下方法，但唔work<br />\n1) 我都射埋一份、互射<br />\n我公司係咁：A請假嗰日就B幫手頂；B請假嗰日就C頂...如此類推，Z請假就A頂⋯<br />\n射波唔係唔得，但我射就要另一個同事幫我做。我唔想累咗無辜嘅同事，要佢捲入我同個仆街嘅鬥爭<br />\n2) 唔做佢嗰份<br />\n之前有次佢又射波，我扮唔記得要做埋佢嗰份、冇做到佢啲野<br />\n但點知被呀頭發現咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3) 同上層反映 俗稱報串<br />\n我老細係唔會開聲話佢，因爲佢態度係唔想理sick leave問題 (驚條仆街去勞工處告公司唔俾人請病假)"},{"pid":"8687aaa5a31fa51d9bc99e3b26df00acaa5d903f","tid":975656,"uid":191815,"like":144,"dislike":1,"score":143,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T22:06:10.000Z","msg":"老細唔出聲<br />\n你咪射埋一份囉"},{"pid":"9cbc16318417f09e9e477c0973842f6cd91e8760","tid":975656,"uid":67203,"like":6,"dislike":95,"score":-89,"quote":{"pid":"8687aaa5a31fa51d9bc99e3b26df00acaa5d903f","tid":975656,"uid":191815,"like":144,"dislike":1,"score":143,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T22:06:10.000Z","msg":"老細唔出聲<br />\n你咪射埋一份囉"},"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T22:09:05.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打回覆 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我唔想累咗其他人<br />\n無理由d罪孽要其他人承受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a34fcc34b5f96f09e64d2dc28599fba09eece41","tid":975656,"uid":191815,"like":135,"dislike":1,"score":134,"quote":{"pid":"9cbc16318417f09e9e477c0973842f6cd91e8760","tid":975656,"uid":67203,"like":6,"dislike":95,"score":-89,"quote":{"pid":"8687aaa5a31fa51d9bc99e3b26df00acaa5d903f","tid":975656,"uid":191815,"like":144,"dislike":1,"score":143,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T22:06:10.000Z","msg":"老細唔出聲<br />\n你咪射埋一份囉"},"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T22:09:05.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打回覆 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我唔想累咗其他人<br />\n無理由d罪孽要其他人承受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T22:10:07.000Z","msg":"你受曬 但係我敢肯定到時有啲咩事 人地唔會記得<br />\n亦唔會有一聲多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"563b756e6ef2936f489d971e850af90f53daef6a","tid":975656,"uid":28624,"like":36,"dislike":1,"score":35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T22:16:38.000Z","msg":"點解要做埋佢果份？<br />\n老細叫就要做？<br />\n老馮架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n淨係叫你又唔叫其他人<br />\n俾人利用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ee2d8a669f64be11b8164929b4cf081c0e29d33","tid":975656,"uid":228846,"like":45,"dislike":1,"score":44,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T22:19:40.000Z","msg":"令到佢 真係要拎sick leave"},{"pid":"143da93f07408b62972089df7bdfabac926451b3","tid":975656,"uid":35746,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T22:24:26.000Z","msg":"有病假紙大晒，射埋一份啦"},{"pid":"fb0906fd1709bf154abf95